No. 11-5087. Jerry Adams, Petitioner v. Michael Corcoran, Superintendent, Woodbourne Correctional Facility. 565 U.S. 934, 132 S. Ct. 382,

181 L. Ed. 2d 241,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6450. October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 416 Fed. Appx. 84.
